Paet 116. Bento with Tamagoyaki today. How is your day? ‚ò∫Ô∏è.

Ingredients
5 eggs
1 tbsp milk
Salt to taste
Dashi powder (optional)
Oil

Fillings
2 tbsp finely diced carrots
Imitation crab
Nori
Scallions

Directions
1. Mix your eggs well with the seasoning and milk.
2. Heat up your pan on medium low. We did not want the eggs to brown too much. Spread the oil and wipe it with a paper towel.
3. Pour 1/5 th of the egg into the pan and cook half way. Begin to roll from one end and leave 3 inches of the omelette to connect with another pour of the egg.
4. Continue until it is done.
#bento #lunch #lunchbox #lunchtime #japanesefood #bentobox
